SUMMARY:Clinton Park to Mt Tabor
DESCRIPTION:Portland Trail Runners\n**New PTR Route!**\n\nJoin us for a run over in SE Portland that highlights Mt Tabor! We will start at Clinton Park off SE Woodward by Franklin HS. From there we will make our steady climb up to Tabor\, taking in some incredible views along the way. Total distance for this one is **6.2 miles** with 657’ gain.\n\n_Note! This route is both paved and trail\, mostly paved._\n\nCheck out the route ahead of time as it is more complex: https://www.strava.com/routes/3465742095239995196\n\n_Want a shorter option?_ Go for the **4.1 mile**\, 456’ gain route here: https://www.strava.com/routes/3465749219665297322\n\nAfterward we willl switch things up and GO GET COFFEE at **Rain or Shine Coffee Shop**\n\nSee you there! ☔️☀️☕️🏃🏽🏃🏻‍♀️
